The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 29th
April, 2002 :-
Shri Ram Vilas Paswan relinquished the charge of the office of
Minister of Coal and Mines; and
i)
The Prime Minister assumed the charge of the office of Minister of
Coal and Mines.
ii)
